lead_paragraph: Sam Burgess has been hailed a lifesaver after the National Rugby League (NRL) player came to the aid of a man who was choking during a fish-eating contest at a Sydney restaurant.

headline.print_headline: Burgess Hailed for Saving Choking Man in Sydney
